desc.title: Desc
examples: Our cancellation protection allows you to reschedule or cancel your booking for a full refund up to 24 hours prior to your reservation. If you decline purchasing this protection, you waive the ability to cancel your reservation and receive any refund. Cancellation protection covers everyone in the current booking.

policy.title: Policy
examples: Your purchase is non-refundable. Rescheduling can be done 24 hours in advance. No cancellations accepted.
